  <li>두번째 (1부터 45까지 리스트를 받아 셔플및 subList실행)</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">public</span> <span class="nc">List</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nc">String</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="nf">buyLotto</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">totalLottoPrice</span><span class="o">){</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="o">(</span><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="o">;</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">getLottoCount</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">totalLottoPrice</span><span class="o">);</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">++){</span>
        <span class="n">lottos</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">add</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="k">new</span> <span class="nc">Lotto</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">getRandomNumbers</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="no">LOTTO_NUMBER_RANGE</span><span class="o">)));</span>
    <span class="o">}</span>
